msgstr "類固醇狂暴"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Roid on steroids'.
#: .\CDDAXP_Effects.json
msgid "Feel the roid rage!!!"
msgstr "感受類固醇的狂怒！！！"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Anabolic comedown, Roid on steroids'.
