#: .\CDDAXP_Ranged.json
msgid ""
"From the flyer: 'The new portable Vulcan!  Enjoy your average ordinary "
"everyday mass destruction!'.  By the way, the 'Miltech 135 Portable Plasma "
"Gatling Minigun' is a 'not so portable' six rotating barrels big fucking "
